8️⃣ Two Ways to Use Action Chains

    Method 1 - Chain Pattern
    ------------------------
    ActionChains(driver).move_to_element(menu).click(submenu).perform()

    All actions written in one line.

    Method 2 - Queue pattern
    ------------------------
    actions = ActionChains(driver)
    actions.move_to_element(menu)
    actions.click()
    actions.peroform()

    Actions are store first , then executed.

9️⃣ Important Action Chain Methods
Method & Description
---------------------
1. click() -> Clicks an element
2. double_click() -> Double clicks an element
3. context_click() -> Right click
4. click_and_hold() -> Hold mouse button
5. release() -> Release mouse button
6. move_to_element() -> Hover over element
7. move_by_offset() -> Move mouse by coordinates
8. drag_and_drop() -> Drag element to another
9. key_down() -> Press key without releasing
10. key_up() -> Release Key
11. send_keys() -> send keyboard input
12. pause() -> Pause actions
13. perform() -> Execute all actions

